				<div><!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_reputation -->
<img class="inlineimg" src="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/forums/images/reputation/reputation_pos.gif" alt="Bree is off the scale" border="0" />
<!-- END TEMPLATE: postbit_reputation --></div>
