		<div>In the old lands (i.e. Pre-Kunark) we pretty much roll on everything.<br />
<br />
But since so much great stuff drops in Kunark, we do the Class Specific items go to the particular classes first, mentality.<br />
<br />
If there's not that class in our group, then we all random for it.<br />
<br />
If it's a semi-specific...(i.e. War, SK, Pal, Cler, Bard), then only those folks who want to roll on it do.  The ALL/ALL stuff is pretty much randomed straight out, unless some groundrules have been laid beforehand.<br />
<br />
Some folks say things like "I don't care about the rest of the drops, I just want XXX loot.  You can have everything else..."<br />
<br />
Braddley Traveler<br />
37.2 Dwarf Cleric<br />
Tarew Marr</div>
